OSCILLATIONS
------------------------------------------------------------

-POSITION

freq = 1.0; //oscillations per second 
amplitude =  90; 
decay =  0;

posCos = Math.abs(Math.cos(freq*time*2*Math.PI));
y = amplitude*posCos/Math.exp(decay*time);
position - [0,y]


- ROTATION

freq = 1;
amp = 80;
amp*Math.sin(freq*time*2*Math.PI);

for position (which needs 2 properties)
